				<div id="head-tag">	




	
				


	
				
																					

				
	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
In Trump plan, Arab Israelis see assault on their identity									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>In a region of clashing national identities, Arab citizens of Israel have long occupied a delicate position straddling two worlds. Now a peace plan is seen as challenging their hard-won gains in Israeli society.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
